MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 107

ESTABLISHING AS HINABIAN-LAWIGAN WATERSHED RESERVATION A PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITIES OF LIBAGON, ST. BERNARD, HINUNANGAN AND SILAGO, PROVINCE OF SOUTHERN LEYTE, PHILIPPINES

